---
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0C447C] mb-4 text-center">See what Lodestar produces.</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">A project dashboard and a portable context file — synthesized automatically from your coding sessions.</p>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start">
      <!-- Dashboard screenshot -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-[#185FA5] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Project Dashboard</div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden bg-white">
          <img src="/dashboard.png" alt="Lodestar project status dashboard showing feature completion, decisions, and session context" class="w-full" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2"><code class="font-mono bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded">lodestar review</code></p>
      </div>

      <!-- .lodestar.md example -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-[#185FA5] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Session Context File</div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden bg-white">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex gap-1.5">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono ml-2">.lodestar.md</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-700 overflow-y-auto max-h-[600px]">
            <div class="text-slate-400 mb-3"># Lodestar Context</div>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <div class="text-[#185FA5] font-semibold mb-2">## Decisions</div>
              <div class="ml-3 space-y-2.5">
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Switched from REST to tRPC</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500">Rationale: Type safety end-to-end. Simpler DX for a solo founder.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Onboarding: email-first, not social auth</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500">Rationale: Devs distrust OAuth popups. Email + magic link converts 2x better.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Ship free tier before Pro</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500">Rationale: Trust and adoption > early revenue.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Drizzle ORM instead of Prisma</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500">Rationale: Prisma cold starts 2-3s on serverless.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <div class="text-[#185FA5] font-semibold mb-2">## Rejected Approaches</div>
              <div class="ml-3 space-y-2.5">
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Prisma ORM</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500">Binary dep caused 2-3s cold starts on Vercel.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">Multi-step onboarding wizard</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-500">40% drop-off at step 2. Replaced with single-screen.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-[#185FA5] font-semibold mb-2">## Open Questions</div>
              <div class="ml-3 space-y-1">
                <div><span class="text-red-500 font-bold">[BLOCKING]</span> Drizzle push or migrate for prod?</div>
                <div><span class="text-slate-400">[non-blocking]</span> Show usage analytics to free users?</div>
                <div><span class="text-slate-400">[non-blocking]</span> Hero: illustration vs terminal screenshot?</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2">Committed to your repo — portable across tools and machines</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
